.DT
remote
$MUDNAME$ player help
remote

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
remote - Echos some text to a specific person.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SP 5 5
remote <person> <text>
.EP

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
Remote takes the text provided and shows it to the person whose name you've
given.  It will appear on their screen with your name prepended to it.
.EP

.SH Example
.SI 5
(If your name is Shiannar)
> remote windy turns you into a frog.

Windy will see:
Shiannar turns you into a frog.
.EI

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
emote, frimble, lsay, position, say, ssay, sayto, soul.
.EP
